 <h3 class="md:text-lg">Book Review: Across the Fence by John Stryker Meyer</h3>
<div class="category-date flex justify-between md:hidden">
<span class="category text-xxs uppercase"></span>
<span class="date text-xxs uppercase">Mar 25</span>
